12 cultural treasures in San Diego, from waterfront venues to modern museums
Finding inspiration is easy in San Diego, where art, history, music, and theater color every neighborhood, from the eclectic city to the balmy beach. Discover emerging artists at beloved museums and markets, explore local history in picturesque surroundings, and catch electric performances set apart by this West Coast gems ever-present sunny day vibes. Fill your San Diego getaway with sights, tunes, and memorable moments that will stay with you with these arts and culture experiences you wont find anywhere else.
